des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your OVAL AIR brand products. Connect Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our OVAL AIR app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure the device in our OVAL AIR app and give your device an appropriate name;
(3) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from your android, iOS or the Amazon app market, then configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(4) Search OVAL AIR skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable OVAL AIR skill, and you'll be navigated to the login page of OVAL AIR;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the air purifier."
"Alexa, turn off the air purifier."
"Alexa, set the fan speed to high." 
"Alexa, set a 2-hour timer."
